t: Al-'aqd al-idari al-su'udi 'ala hawu nitam al-munafasat wa-al-mushtarayat al-hukumiyah wa-al-lauihah al-tanfidhiyah
Wafau al-wafa bi-akhbar dar al-musaafa salla allah 'alayhi wa-sallam
Al-mawsu'ah al-jinauiyah al-hadithah fi sharh qanun al-'uqubat aibqan li-ahdath al-ta'dilat al-sadirah bi-al-qanun raqam 95 li-sanat 2003
Huquq al-lajiuin al-filisainiyin bayna al-shar'iyah al-duwaliyah wa-al-mufawahat al-filasainiyah-al-israuiliyah
Dalil al-shirau kharij iaar al-safaqat al-'umumiyah
Al-tadakhkhul al-duwali al-insani bayna mithaq al-umam al-muttahidah wa-al-taabiq al-'amali
واقع ظاهرة إنحراف الأحداث في دولة الإمارات العربية المتحدة
